Living with one Move (31)
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0\deflang1033\deflangfe1042{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par \b White to play\b0 .
\par In an instant, capturing Black's one stone looks good.
\par
\par However one shouldn't decide it without reading whether it is good or not.
\par Is it pae or White can live unconditionally?
\par
\par
\par }
