Dia. 01 Life?
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red255\green0\blue0;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par Anybody can think about capturing with 1. The important thing is if this move is good or not.
\par
\par If Black plays dansu at 2, White lives easily with 3.
\par
\par However this variation is White's \cf1\b wishful thinking\cf0\b0 .
\par In other words, Black is not going to play at 2.
\par }
