Dia. 02 Pae
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red255\green0\blue0;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par Black can play at 1 to break the eye. In the previous diagram, White played here and lived.
\par Yes, there we go! "\cf1\b The opponent's vital point is my vital point\cf0\b0 ."
\par
\par After White's strongest answer at 2, Black makes pae with 3.\cf1\b
\par }
