Dia. 03 Correct Answer
[{\rtf1\ansi\ansicpg949\deff0{\fonttbl{\f0\fnil\fcharset129 \'b1\'bc\'b8\'b2;}}
{\colortbl ;\red255\green0\blue0;}
\viewkind4\uc1\pard\lang1042\f0\fs18
\par White 1 at the \cf1\b 1-2 point\cf0\b0  is the only vital point for living.
\par It was the \cf1\b opponent's vital point\cf0\b0  too.
\par
\par After Black 2, White lives with two eyes with 3.
\par
\par It wasn't a difficult problem, but White has to be careful with the pae.
\par }
